unittitle_ssm: Frederick and Ann Dunekack family photographs and property records
abstract_ssm: The collection consists of photographs and property records which belonged to Frederick and Ann Dunekack (of Brooklyn, New York). The photographs document buildings and businesses throughout Brooklyn, circa 1904. The property records relate to land located in the southern part of the Williamsburg neighborhood of Brooklyn, dating from 1863 to 1907.
